<app cb:word-count="55" from="#beg0219014" to="#end0219014"><lem wit="#wit1"><item>琝<note n="0219015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝荼【元】</note><app n="0219015"><lem wit="#wit1">茶</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit4">荼</rdg></app>財食自長聞法悟解一</item><item>郁伽見佛<lb n="0219b23" ed="T"/>其醉自醒受戒以妻施人二</item><item>魚身得富緣<lb n="0219b24" ed="T"/>三</item><item>闍<note n="0219016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＝利【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0219016"><lem wit="#wit1">梨</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit3 #wit4 #wit5">利</rdg></app>兄弟以法獲財終不散失四<lb n="0219b25" ed="T"/></item><item>居士子大意<note n="0219017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig">〔以〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0219017"><lem wit="#wit1">以</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit3 #wit4 #wit5"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>求明珠五</item></lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0219018" to="#end0219018"><lem wit="#wit1">茶</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit4 #wit2">荼</rdg></app>
